{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/diesel-rs/diesel/issues/857","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/diesel-rs/diesel","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/diesel-rs/diesel/issues/857/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/diesel-rs/diesel/issues/857/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/diesel-rs/diesel/issues/857/events","html_url":"https://github.com/diesel-rs/diesel/issues/857","id":221409511,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWUyMjE0MDk1MTE=","number":857,"title":"diesel_cli doesn't fully respect MIGRATION_DIRECTORY","user":{"login":"matt4682","id":11151039,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjExMTUxMDM5","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/11151039?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/matt4682","html_url":"https://github.com/matt4682","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/matt4682/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/matt4682/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/matt4682/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/matt4682/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/matt4682/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/matt4682/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/matt4682/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/matt4682/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/matt4682/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":254193212,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwyNTQxOTMyMTI=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/diesel-rs/diesel/labels/bug","name":"bug","color":"fc2929","default":true,"description":null}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2017-04-12T22:34:50Z","updated_at":"2017-05-14T17:37:06Z","closed_at":"2017-05-14T17:37:06Z","author_association":"NONE","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"When creating and running migrations through `diesel migration generate` and `diesel migration run`, diesel_cli looks at the `MIGRATION_DIRECTORY` environment variable and uses that as shown [here](https://github.com/diesel-rs/diesel/blob/897fac76bcdd1da2596ab74e9dd627b083381b70/diesel_cli/src/main.rs#L114).\r\n\r\nHowever when you run `diesel setup`, it will only [search for](https://github.com/diesel-rs/diesel/blob/368674c8f25de2b986af062e1ff0a7d42ea88501/diesel/src/migrations/mod.rs#L255) and [create](https://github.com/diesel-rs/diesel/blob/897fac76bcdd1da2596ab74e9dd627b083381b70/diesel_cli/src/main.rs#L148) the default migrations directory.\r\n\r\nAdditionally running `diesel database setup` uses the `run_pending_migrations` function which also only [looks at](https://github.com/diesel-rs/diesel/blob/368674c8f25de2b986af062e1ff0a7d42ea88501/diesel/src/migrations/mod.rs#L95) the default migrations directory, so migrations won't be run if they are configured and stored somewhere else.\r\n\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"Eijebong","id":3650385,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM2NTAzODU=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3650385?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Eijebong","html_url":"https://github.com/Eijebong","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Eijebong/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Eijebong/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Eijebong/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Eijebong/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Eijebong/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Eijebong/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Eijebong/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Eijebong/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.gi